    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound driver\u2019s specimen featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies. Mated to a desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, it delivers a visceral, analog driving experience with a 333 hp output and an 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis is well-sorted, featuring a reinforced rear subframe and the factory M Variable Differential Lock for superior lateral grip. Maintenance is up to date with the VANOS system serviced and rod bearings addressed, ensuring the longevity of the valvetrain and bottom end. While it carries the honest patina of an enjoyed performance vehicle, the suspension geometry remains tight and the throttle response is sharp, making it an ideal candidate for the enthusiast who prioritizes mechanical integrity and longitudinal dynamics.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
