    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of the high-revving S54 platform. The 3.2L inline-six features individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS, delivering a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M-differential lock. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement, a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, and structural reinforcement of the rear subframe mounting points. The chassis retains its factory-spec MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension with updated bushings for precise lateral stability. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain and cooling system are optimized for performance longevity. A well-sorted enthusiast machine with documented valve adjustments.",
